'''喬治亞飲食'''（{{lang-ka|ქართული სამზარეულო}}）是指[[喬治亞|喬治亞]]獨特的飲食文化。喬治亞地處鏈接歐亞大陸的貿易路線的中繼點，因此飲食受到多個地區的影響。喬治亞飲食的特點是做法及食材多樣，且較多使用香料<ref>Food Cultures of the World Encyclopedia, Volume 1, Ken Albala, p. 125</ref>。20世紀之後，由於史達林等喬治亞裔俄羅斯人偏好喬治亞食物，喬治亞飲食開始在俄羅斯國內普及。現在俄羅斯幾乎所有城市都有喬治亞餐館<ref>Food Culture in Russia and Central Asia, Glenn Randall Mack, Asele Surina, p. 10</ref>。喬治亞具代表性的食品包括[[奇克美露里|奇克美露里]]、[[阿賈普桑達利|阿賈普桑達利]]、[[巴德里亞尼|巴德里亞尼]]、[[戈吉納基|戈吉納基]]、[[奇希爾圖馬|奇希爾圖馬]]、[[查納基|查納基]]、[[羅比奧_(食品)|羅比奧]]、[[卡爾喬_(食品)|卡爾喬]]、[[卡里餃|卡里餃]]、[[丘爾其赫拉|丘爾其赫拉]]、[[起司麵包|起司麵包]]等。喬治亞人自8000年前就開始釀造[[葡萄酒|葡萄酒]]，是葡萄酒的發明國，已有8000年的釀酒歷史<ref name="Vinologue">{{citation|title=Georgia: A guide to the cradle of wine|author=Miquel Hudin & Daria Kholodolina|publisher=[[Vinologue|Vinologue]]|isbn=978-1941598054|year=2017|pages=300|url=http://www.vinologue.com/books/georgia/|accessdate=2021-03-29|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926092851/https://www.vinologue.com/books/georgia/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://cycloscope.weebly.com/blog/traditional-winemaking-in-georgia-the-oldest-wine-in-the-world |title=Archived copy |access-date=2015-04-15 |url-status=yes |archive-url=https://archive.is/20150415080208/http://cycloscope.weebly.com/blog/traditional-winemaking-in-georgia-the-oldest-wine-in-the-world |archive-date=2015-04-15 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2010/WORLD/europe/04/20/georgia.wine.heritage/|title=Unearthing Georgia's wine heritage|first=Ivan|last=Watson|publisher=CNN|access-date=21 February 2018|archive-date=2010-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100429114827/http://edition.cnn.com/2010/WORLD/europe/04/20/georgia.wine.heritage/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=Cultures of The World Georgia|last1=Spilling |first1=Michael |last2=Wong |first2=Winnie |year=2008 |isbn=978-0-7614-3033-9 |page=128 }}</ref>。[[喬治亞葡萄酒|喬治亞葡萄酒]]在世界享有盛譽。

